Package: rebalancedNoise
Title: Perturbative SDC for Magnitude Tables (EZS Method)
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
  person(
    given="Bernhard", family="Meindl", 
    email="bernhard.meindl@statistik.gv.at", 
    role=c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Implements the EZS method for perturbative statistical
    disclosure control as described in Almberg (2025), "Using perturbative
    methods for magnitude tables in statistical disclosure control"
    presented at UNECE
    <https://www.unece.org/sites/default/files/2025-10/SDC2025_Sf_Sweden_Almberg_D.pdf>.
    The package provides an R6-based engine that applies record-level noise
    with a dynamic rebalancing algorithm to ensure high data quality and
    internal additivity within table hierarchies.
